Return & Refund Policy

Last updated on 27-04-2026 19:15:03

CM Filings believes in helping its customers as far as possible, and has therefore a liberal return and refund policy. Under this policy:

• Returns will be considered only if the request is made immediately after availing our service. However, the return request may not be entertained if the work has already been initiated or submitted to the relevant authorities.

CM Filings does not accept return requests for services once the process has been completed or documents have been submitted, as these are non-refundable. However, refund/replacement can be made if the customer establishes that there was an error on our part.

• In case of any error in documents or services provided, please report the same to our Customer Support team. The request will be entertained once our team has reviewed and verified the issue. This should be reported within only 1 day of availing the service. Our Customer Support Team after looking into your complaint will take an appropriate decision.

• For services related to government filing or third-party platforms, any delays or rejections caused by external authorities are beyond our control. In such cases, we will assist you in resubmission or rectification as per applicable norms.

• In case of any refunds approved by CM Filings, it'll take 1-2 days for the refund to be processed to the original payment method.

If you have any questions regarding our Return & Refund Policy, please contact our support team at support@cmfilings.com or +91 9946151111.